name: Unownable NFT
description: Unownable Token (U0T) is a new concept and allows you to possess something temporarily without owning it. Like a ball in a never-ending game that's always passed around, never staying with one person.
prompt: Create a physical abstract painting together with a kid, triadic colors with white, 4:3, expressive, freedom, no mistakes. Create a digital image of the physical painting, flash lighting, 4:3. Turn the digital image into a physical oil painting.
